    • Field Detail

      • PRIMITIVE

        public static final JsonpValueFactory PRIMITIVE
        A singleton instance of JsonpValueFactory.

        This factory uses NumberBuilder.build(text,true) to parse JSON→URL numbers.

      • DOUBLE

        public static final JsonpValueFactory DOUBLE
        A singleton instance of JsonpValueFactory.

        This factory uses Double.valueOf(text) to parse JSON→URL numbers.

      • BIGMATH

        public static final JsonpValueFactory BIGMATH
        A singleton instance of JsonpValueFactory.

        This factory uses new BigInteger() or new BigDecimal() to parse JSON→URL numbers.

        Description copied from interface: ValueFactory
        construct a new JSON array from the given builder.

        Some implementations implement the builder pattern and separate arrays from things that build arrays. This method accepts an array builder and returns an array. For implementations that do not separate arrays from builders this may be the identity function.
